Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.14,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:36.97,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.86,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.00,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:22.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:27.08,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:34.02,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You shameless bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That song is the one I hate the most in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,24. Encore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she say she hates it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew perfectly well it was her favorite piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she get so upset when I played it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The 12-minute-after train is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't been back since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know, don't ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,About Saint-Juste-sama and Miya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, though I can't understand the world they share...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...I know that their kind of world frightens me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As I see the increasing gloom in Saint-Juste's eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the rage hidden behind Miya-sama's kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...I understand their world less and less.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The 25-after bus! The 25-after bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My first-period English teacher, Kusunoki, is very strict!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always telling you, don't smoke in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I do it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... play this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That music!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still upset over yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might know something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This violin music...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That piece... once... was one Fukiko practiced very hard on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a freshman then... Six years ago, in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Six years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that summer very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We stayed at the vacation house, near the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi visited us there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi Takehiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Though he only stayed for one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When summer ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...we had a farewell party, inviting the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi promised that he'd be back for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, he'd be back, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when Fukiko suddenly started practicing that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was going to play it at the farewell party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She practiced hard everyday, sometimes until midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have really been looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked my opinion of it over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At the party, Fukiko did play that violin piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And what beautiful playing it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard to believe it was being played by a 12 year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi heard it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he never showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He called right before the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He said there was an emergency, and he couldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When she finished playing, the guests applauded with admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They were even asking for an encore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An encore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But she didn't respond with an encore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but she never played that piece again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Never?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact I haven't even seen her pick up a violin since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you hear that song, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think back, it was only when she was alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...or no one else was around, that she would play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched from the distance, without being noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, did Henmi visit often?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'm fairly certain... that was the first and last visit he made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I met with Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to the university to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Any special reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We just had a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On what subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,About 6 years ago, at our vacation home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And about Henmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A single ugly rose has vulgarized this whole arrangement!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That damned girl... this is not her business!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You were practicing that song just for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for him, for Henmi Takehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You put your heart in it, you put your soul in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know! I really didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first met him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi... Takehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous here! I told you not to come here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you to a classmate from school, Henmi Takehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my sister, Fukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Henmi. Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be staying here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, everything seemed aglow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...as if everything took place in a warm dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I compare thee to a summer's day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Thou art more lovely and more temperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rough winds do shake the darling buds of May...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a book of Shakespeare's poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakespeare?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have to write a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, read some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please read something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...the poem that you like the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rough winds do shake the darling buds of May,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And summer's lease...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...hath all too short a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no use... it's just as bad as outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please read that poem once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I compare thee to a summer's day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Thou art more lovely and more temperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rough winds do shake the darling buds of May,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And summer's lease hath all too short a date,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometime too hot the eye of heaven shines,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and often is his gold complexion dimm'd,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And every fair from fair sometime declines,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,By chance, or nature's changing course, untrimm'd,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But the eternal summer shall not fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,not lose possession of that beauty thou possessest,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,nor shall Death brag thou wander'st in his shade,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When in eternal lines to time thou growest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this poem as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The book is yours, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true what I heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really leaving tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I promise I'll be back for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you promise me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweetest, brightest day of my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The same song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here very often?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I... I did when Saint-Juste-sama caught a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...several times, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But since then, I haven't—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I warn you back then to not get involved with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Miya-sama become so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being in her room isn't reason enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That song... it must somehow be the song...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only 12. But my heart died on that summer's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We have so many guests here tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since you're going to play the violin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...twice as many people came this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My red shoes! Tonight I need my red shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this look good? Red shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Looks great. Are they new?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I got them especially for tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment, Fukiko. There was a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That just can't be true, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He had some kind of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Until this morning, he was planning to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But... he made a promise to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them all the results of all your practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After tonight, I'll be known as the brother of a violin prodigy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I played on in desperation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With a pleasant smile, even...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...despite the thorns that were piercing my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer night's party, in my 12th year...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...my first and last happiness died forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was magnificent, Miss Fukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me! I won't forgive you if you follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I compare thee to a summer's day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Thou art more lovely and more temperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But thy eternal summer shall not fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor shall Death brag thou wander'st in his shade,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In eternal lines to time thou growest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In eternal lines to time thou growest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That sweetest day, that summers day,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...even if I was betrayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...it is mine, forever mine, and mine alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...until the day that he returns with me to that summer's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow anyone else to have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.66,0:24:13.86,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:19.33,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:24.94,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.94,0:24:30.41,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:36.69,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.69,0:24:42.16,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.16,0:24:44.89,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.89,0:24:47.70,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.70,0:24:50.10,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.10,0:24:55.37,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.98,0:25:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko suddenly summons Nanako to the Sorority House.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She approaches, drawing her lips close to Nanako's ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.13,0:25:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...when Rei suddenly rushes in, and reveals a secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.74,0:25:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...which gives Nanako the shock of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.66,0:25:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Crimson Lipstick
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.53,0:25:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
